    dc:description "FIGURES 13–15. Male hypopygium, lateral view. 13. Amblypsilopus marginatus sp. nov.; 14. Amblypsilopus medogensis sp. nov.; 15. Amblypsilopus quinquepetalus sp. nov. Scale bar = 0.2 mm. Abbreviations: epn = epandrium, hyp = hypandrium, ph = phallus, sur = surstylus, lat = lateral lobe, cer = cercus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2628508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2628506>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–12. Male hypopygium, lateral view. 10. Amblypsilopus acuminatus sp. nov.; 11. Amblypsilopus liangi sp. nov.; 12. Amblypsilopus liratus sp. nov. Scale bar = 0.2 mm. Abbreviations: epn = epandrium, hyp = hypandrium, ph = phallus, sur = surstylus, lat = lateral lobe, cer = cercus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2628506/files/figure.png" ;
